6 months of #SanjFoundDave ❤️

A few weeks before our wedding @sam_and_ekta asked us to write letters to each other, and we read these for the first time moments before walking to the mandap. And it looked something like this-

Watching this makes me feel all those same emotions again- the goosebumps, the excitement, the gratitude and the incredible happiness I felt to be marrying you amongst our closest family and friends who braved the odds to be there. ❤️
